Begin deadSarethiGuard

;script to enable dead guards in Sarethi Manor during HR_GuardSarethi

if ( GetJournalIndex HR_GuardSarethi >= 100 )
	if ( GetDisabled == 0 )
		Disable
	endif
	Return
endif

if ( GetJournalIndex HR_GuardSarethi == 0 )
	if ( GetDisabled == 0 )
		Disable
	endif
	Return
endif

if ( GetDisabled == 1 )
	Enable
endif

End
